INSERT INTO `cartas` VALUES ('1', 'Predefinida 1', 'Carta a Uruguayos', '', 'Conferencistas', '<table width=\"700\"  border=\"0\" align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"color:#000000; font-size:13px; font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif\">\r\n		  <tr>\r\n			<td><div align=\"justify\">\r\n <p align=\"right\">Montevideo, 22 de Octubre de 2010</p>\r\n <p><br>\r\n							<br>\r\n						  Estimado <:profesion> <:nombre> <:apellidos><br>\r\n						  Presente.</p>En nombre de la Asociaci&oacute;n Panamericana de Infectolog&iacute;a (API) nos complace en comunicarle que nuestro pa&iacute;s ha sido elegido como sede del XV Congreso Panamericano de Infectolog&iacute;a, a realizarse del 7 al 11 de abril de 2011 en Punta del Este- Uruguay.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	\r\n	Es un honor para el comit&eacute; cient&iacute;fico del congreso invitarlo a participar dentro del programa cient&iacute;fico del mismo.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Si usted acepta la invitaci&oacute;n en los pr&oacute;ximos d&iacute;as recibir&aacute; el detalle de vuestra participaci&oacute;n.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Asimismo solicitamos que nos confirme vuestra aceptaci&oacute;n antes del 30 de octubre del corriente.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Sera un gran honor poder contar con su presencia en el XV Congreso Panamericano de Infectolog&iacute;a<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n			  <p style=\"padding-left:30px\">				    <strong><img src=\"http://api2011.easyplanners.info/programa/img/firma.jpg\" width=\"153\" height=\"89\"><br>\r\n			    \r\n			    Dr. Julio Medina <br>\r\n			    Cordinador del Comit&eacute; Cientifico </strong></p></div></td>\r\n		  </tr>\r\n		   <tr>\r\n		<td width=\"46%\" height=\"26\" align=\"right\"><strong>Por m&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n <a href=\"\'.$paginaINFOlink.\'\">haga clic aqu&iacute;</a></strong></td>\r\n		 </tr>\r\n	  <tr align=\"center\">\r\n		<td height=\"27\" align=\"right\"><strong>Programa Online <a href=\"http://api2011.easyplanners.info/programa/\">clic aqu&iacute;</a></strong></td>\r\n	  </tr>\r\n	  <tr align=\"center\">\r\n	    <td align=\"left\">Si acepto<br>\r\n        <br>\r\n        No acepto</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n	</table>', '0');
INSERT INTO `cartas` VALUES ('2', 'Predefinida 2', 'Carta en Ingl&eacute;s', '', 'Conferencistas', '<table width=\"700\"  border=\"0\" align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"color:#000000; font-size:13px; font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif\">\r\n				  <tr>\r\n					<td><div align=\"justify\">\r\n					  <p align=\"right\">Montevideo, October 18<sup>th</sup> 2010</p>\r\n						  <p><strong><br>\r\n							<br>\r\n						  </strong>Dear <:profesion> <:nombre> <:apellidos>:</p>\r\n					  <p>On behalf of the Pan American Association of Infectious Diseases (API), we\r\n	are pleased to inform you that our country has been chosen to host the XV\r\n	Pan American Congress of Infectious Diseases, which is going to be held\r\n	from April 7 to 11, 2011 in Punta del Este  Uruguay.<br>\r\n	<strong><br>\r\n	</strong>It is an honor for our Scientific Committee to invite you to take part in the scientific activities that we are scheduling.<strong><br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	</strong>If you accept the invitation, in the forthcoming weeks you will receive the details about your participation in the congress,as well as travel details. Please,send to us your feedback before october 30, 2010.<br>\r\n	We would feel very honored if you could join the XV Panamerican Congress on Infectious Diseases.<strong><br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Kind regards, </strong></p>\r\n					  <p style=\"padding-left:30px\">				    <strong><img src=\"http://api2011.easyplanners.info/programa/img/firma.jpg\" width=\"153\" height=\"89\"><br>\r\n	\r\n					  Dr. Julio Medina <br>\r\n					  Coordinator Scientific  Committe </strong></p>\r\n					</div></td>\r\n				  </tr>\r\n				   <tr>\r\n				<td width=\"46%\" align=\"right\"><strong>For more information <a href=\"\'.$paginaINFOlink.\'\">\'.$paginaINFO.\'</a></strong></td>\r\n				 </tr>\r\n			  <tr align=\"center\">\r\n				<td align=\"right\"><strong>Online Program <a href=\"http://api2011.easyplanners.info/programa/\">click here</a></strong></td>\r\n			  </tr>\r\n			</table>', '0');
