INSERT INTO `cartas` VALUES ('11', 'Nueva Predefinida 1', 'Speek Extranjero SIN sociedad', '', 'Conferencistas', '<table width=\"700\"  border=\"0\" align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"color:#000000; font-size:13px; font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif\">\r\n				  <tr>\r\n					<td>\r\n					  <p align=\"right\"><:fecha></p>\r\n					  <p align=\"left\"><strong><br>\r\n							<br>\r\n						  </strong>Dear <:profesion> <:nombre> <:apellidos><br><br>\r\n						  The Scientific Committee of the XV Pan American Congress of Infectious Diseases, which is going to be held in Punta del Este, Uruguay from 7 to 11 April 2011, has the honor to invite you to participate in the scientific program according to the activity described at the bottom of this letter. <br><br>\r\n					  As usual, the organizing committee will take charge of your flight ticket, accommodation and your registration to the Congress. </p>\r\n					      <p align=\"left\">In the next month you will received the details of your stay in Uruguay. </p>\r\n					      <p align=\"left\">Below is a form to complete and forward it to <a href=\"mailto:info@apiuruguay.com\">info@apiuruguay.com</a>  as fast as possible with your current photo for inclusion on the web.</p>\r\n					      <p align=\"left\">Please go to: (<a href=\"http://www.apiuruguay.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=27&Itemid=&#9001;=en\">http://www.apiuruguay.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=27&Itemid=&#9001;=en</a>) and read the regulations for participants. It is important know the way that the activities are going to be held. </p>\r\n					      <p align=\"left\">On behalf of the Scientific Committee of the XV Pan American Congress of Infectious Diseases, will be an honor to receive in our country.</p>\r\n					      <p align=\"left\"><strong><br>\r\n				          Yours sincerely, </strong></p>\r\n				      <p style=\"padding-left:30px\">				    <strong><img src=\"http://api2011.easyplanners.info/programa/img/firma.jpg\" width=\"153\" height=\"89\"><br>\r\n	\r\n					  Dr. Julio Medina <br>\r\n					  Coordinator Scientific  Committe </strong></p><br><br><br><br>\r\n                      <p><strong>Form:</strong></p>\r\n                      <p>A.	Passport:</p>\r\n                      <p>B.	Name (as shown in Passport):</p>\r\n                      <p>C.	Availability to attend the conference:<br>\r\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"color:#000000; font-size:13px; font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif\">\r\n                          <tr><td>Wednesday 6</td><td>   </td><td>Yes:</td><td>      </td><td>No:</td><td>      </td></tr>\r\n                          <tr><td><strong>Thursday 7</strong></td>\r\n                      <td><strong>   </strong></td>\r\n                  <td><strong>Yes:</strong></td>\r\n          <td><strong>      </strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>No:</strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>      </strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n                          <tr><td><strong>Friday 8</strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>   </strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>Yes:</strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>      </strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>No:</strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>      </strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n                          <tr><td><strong>Saturday 9</strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>   </strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>Yes:</strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>      </strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>No:</strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>      </strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n                          <tr><td><strong>Sunday 10</strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>   </strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>Yes:</strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>      </strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>No:</strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>      </strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n                          <tr><td><strong>Monday 11</strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>   </strong></td>\r\n        <td><strong>Yes:</st