\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">The\r\nScientific Committee of the XV Pan American Congress of Infectious Diseases,\r\nwhich is going to be held in Punta del Este, Uruguay from 7 to 11 April 2011,\r\nhas the honor to invite you to participate in the scientific program according\r\nto the <span class=\"shorttext\">activity described</span> at the bottom of this\r\nletter. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">As usual, your society will pay for your flight\r\nticket. The organizing committee will take charge of your accommodation and\r\nregistration to the Congress. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"ES-UY\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">In the next month you will received the details of\r\nyour stay in Uruguay. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"ES-UY\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">Below is a form to complete and forward it to <a href=\"mailto:info@apiuruguay.com\">info@apiuruguay.com</a> <span style=\"\">&nbsp;</span>as fast as possible with your current photo\r\nfor inclusion on the web.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">Please go to (</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"ES-UY\"><a href=\"http://www.apiuruguay.com/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27&amp;Itemid=&amp;lang=en\"><span style=\"\" lang=\"EN-US\">http://www.apiuruguay.com/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27&amp;Itemid=&amp;lang=en</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"ES-UY\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">)\r\nand read the regulations for participants. It is important know the way that\r\nthe activities are going to be held. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;\" lang=\"ES-UY\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">On behalf of the Scientific Committee of the XV Pan\r\nAmerican Congress of Infectious Diseases, will be an honor to receive in our\r\ncountry.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"ES-UY\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">Yours <span class=\"shorttext\">sincerely, </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">Dr. Julio Medina</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">Scientific Committee Coordinator</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"ES-UY\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: &quot;Gisha&quot;,&quot;sans-s