INSERT INTO `cartas` VALUES ('12', 'Nueva Predefinidas 2', 'Speek Extranjero CON sociedad', '', 'Conferencistas', '<table width=\"700\"  border=\"0\" align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"color:#000000; font-size:13px; font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif\">\r\n				  <tr>\r\n					<td>\r\n					  <p align=\"right\"><:fecha></p>\r\n					  <p align=\"left\"><strong><br>\r\n							<br>\r\n						  </strong>Dear <:profesion> <:nombre> <:apellidos><br><br></p>\r\n					      <p>The Scientific Committee of the XV Pan American Congress of Infectious Diseases, which is going to be held in Punta del Este, Uruguay from 7 to 11 April 2011, has the honor to invite you to participate in the scientific program according to the activity described at the bottom of this letter. <br><br>\r\n					        As usual, your society will pay for your flight ticket. The organizing committee will take charge of your accommodation and registration to the Congress. </p>\r\n					      <p>In the next month you will received the details of your stay in Uruguay. </p>\r\n					      <p>Below is a form to complete and forward it to <a href=\"mailto:info@apiuruguay.com\">info@apiuruguay.com</a>  as fast as possible with your current photo for inclusion on the web.</p>\r\n					      <p>Please go to (<a href=\"http://www.apiuruguay.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=27&Itemid=&lang=en\">http://www.apiuruguay.com/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27&amp;Itemid=&amp;lang=en</a>) and read the regulations for participants. It is important know the way that the activities are going to be held. </p>\r\n					      <p>On behalf of the Scientific Committee of the XV Pan American Congress of Infectious Diseases, will be an honor to receive in our country.</p>\r\n					      <p align=\"left\"><strong><br>\r\n				          Yours sincerely, </strong></p>\r\n				      <p style=\"padding-left:30px\">				    <strong><img src=\"http://api2011.easyplanners.info/program